modName: No Rocks by the well in Whiterun
summary: Removed the small pile of rocks next to the well in Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
Are you sick of coming out of Belethor\'s Shop after selling off some of your goods, only to see what appears to be a dead body next to the well?  Then you remember that it\'s just a pile of rocks?  Then this mod is for you.


Just drop the esp into the data folder and activate it as usual.
author: bobglaub
